{"tid":1305887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支線小任務-帶好風向 減少誤導] 知唔知有咩慘過開post瘋狂被屌同瘋狂負評?","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:00.000Z","uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"777dfcdde3fa219fcea97268561ca3b570a949b8","tid":1305887,"uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"知道會有好多3毛, 假膠, Attention whores會出post擾亂風向. 所以喺都提議下各位手足如何可以減低佢哋嘅影響.<br />\n<br />\n知唔知有咩慘過開post或留comment瘋狂被屌同瘋狂負評?<br />\n就係出咗post或留comment之後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>0回覆0負評</strong></span></span>充其量只有小量正評<br />\n<br />\n係就係咁簡單, 大家上連登同時一齊做一個支線小任務: 睇到有似乎有問題嘅post或comment: 例如<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>分化</strong></span></span>, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">惡意挑釁</span></span>, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>擾亂視線</strong></span></span>, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>假消息</strong></span></span>... <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>盡量一致性地忍住唔比任何反應, 忽略佢哋.</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其中有少少心理分析可以講下:<br />\n你瘋狂屌同瘋狂負評一D有問題嘅post或comment, 係, 你出咗氣, 但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問題係你亦同時比咗回應佢</strong></span></span>. 你覺得班人真係會希望出個有問題嘅post或comment係會諗住過千正評, 一堆人支持? 唔會㗎嘛, 你一瘋狂屌同瘋狂負評佢, 之後佢出於報復心又好不忿又好得到存在感又好, 你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>變相鼓勵佢再玩多D</strong></span></span>.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>0回覆0負評</strong></span></span>就唔同啦, 佢根本唔知大家有咩反應, 佢之後可能都會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>短期内</strong></span></span>再瘋狂出一堆相同post或comment, 但一旦佢長期被忽略, 佢根本唔知佢下一步應該點. 原因好簡單: 冇癮. 出完post好似冇出過咁, 佢有連登Ac同冇都冇任何分別.<br />\n<br />\n其實block user都有差不多功能, 但你block得幾多? 但大家做到一齊忽略個效果就大好多啦.<br />\n另外, 唔比反應仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>另一好處</strong></span></span>: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>避免誤傷同路人</strong></span></span>, 有時可能對方一時唔理解或者get錯, 你暫時冇比回應令成件事有灣轉, 唔會令大家咁易<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩極化</strong></span></span>, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連比人認錯歸隊嘅機會都冇</strong></span></span>.<br />\n<br />\n所以由今日起一齊做一個支線小任務: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">忽略所有有睇落有問題嘅post或comment!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5fc24f8a76d9779114709d096e79fbcc95b4cd23","tid":1305887,"uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"忽略所有有睇落有問題嘅post或comment!"},{"pid":"243b3d1d058e540e83c07c52d4098e01e102cf33","tid":1305887,"uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"忽略所有有睇落有問題嘅post或comment!"}]}